  "doc_id": "18705",
  "text": "In [CITATION_1] a fuzzy based agent was proposed to rank recommended candidates' CVs within recruitment systems. Fuzzy logic was used to model the candidate preferences of the selection board members and also to resolve the uncertainty and conflict in the group decision making. A fuzzy based method that improves the collaborative filtering efficiency for multiple collaborating users was proposed in [CITATION_2] . In this system fuzzy sets were used to model the user bias and uncertainty which result from multiple user interaction.",
